---
title: Crispy Old Bay Tilapia & Spicy Remoulade with Corn on the Cob, Potato Wedges & Red Cabbage Slaw
description: Crispy Old Bay-seasoned tilapia stars in this coastal-inspired meal, paired with a creamy, spicy remoulade for dipping. On the side: sweet corn on the cob, golden potato wedges, and a tangy red cabbage and carrot slaw for crunch. It’s a bold, satisfying plate that brings the flavor of a seafood shack home.
